    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Do you love the ocean?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into Sea of Peridot and live your own ocean life!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build a self-sufficient life through aquaculture and fishing, or connect and cooperate with local villagers. Strike profitable deals through fierce haggling, travel between charming towns, and collect unforgettable memories along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Craving an escape from daily life?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set sail into uncharted waters! Encounter unexpected events, explore countless islands, and uncover hidden treasures. You might even meet a few special friends on your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ready to make it your own?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your outfits, your island, and even the sea itself. Use what you’ve gathered to craft something meaningful or simply splurge for fun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enjoy your ocean life, your way.</strong> </p>",
